ing: 1 (1.5 fluid ounce) jigger Swiss chocolate almond liqueur
1 (1.5 fluid ounce) jigger white chocolate liqueur
des: "Super yummy!  It can either be a tall cool drink or a blended frappe - but look out or they'll sneak up on you!"
ins: In a tall glass over ice, pour the Swiss almond chocolate liqueur and white chocolate liqueur. Fill glass with milk; stir and serve.
